s of 20-25Msun stars, black hole formation in this mass range\nprovides a natural explanation of the red supergiant problem.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Jul 2014 20:00:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-22"}
