ommon drop in metal mass fractions within the inner ~200kpc of the cool cores,\nwhich is due to a combination of wind suppression by outer pressure within our\nmodel and a lack of mixing after the formation of these dense regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Jul 2014 05:12:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-17"}
